SELECT transparency_and_accountability.ai_system_name, accountability_record.reviewed_by FROM transparency_and_accountability LEFT JOIN accountability_record ON transparency_and_accountability.id = accountability_record.ai_system_id WHERE transparency_and_accountability.transparency_score > 70;
